{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">理解弹性势能的概念；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">探究弹性势能的表达式。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">弹力做的功等于弹性势能的变化量。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">刻度尺、弹簧测力计、一端固定的弹簧</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.向右拖动弹簧测力计一小段距离，点击记录将数据记录到表格中；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.重复刚才的步骤再做</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次，将结果记录到表格中；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.点击表格属性，选择显示图象；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4.在图象中选择合适的类型及数据，做出</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><em>F</em></span>-<em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">x</span></em><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">图象。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">弹性势能表达式为<em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">E</span></em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">p</span><em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">=kx</span></em><sup>2</sup>/2。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">弹力做正功，弹性势能减小；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">弹力做负功，弹性势能增加；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">弹力做的功等于弹性势能的变化量。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}